Structural Divergence Analysis

Maria Laura Marcos, Julian Echave

Introduction

In this case we studied the fabp family. We used as reference for the ENM the protein with pdb code 1hmt. We simulated 10 mutants of this reference for each protein of the family. The fabp family is of the type beta and consists of the following proteins:

##  [1] "1lif"  "1pmpa" "1fdqa" "1opba" "1ggla" "1cbs"  "1cbia" "1ftpa"
##  [9] "1eioa" "3ifba" "1b56"  "1bwya" "1crb"  "1mdc"  "1lfo"  "1ifc"
